"title": "8416: encouragement, promises of God's",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8416: encouragement, promises of god's",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God promises continual support for his people, particularly when they become weary, depressed or disillusioned.</p>\n<h2>God's encouragement affirmed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:17-Ps10:18\">PSA 10:17–10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:20-Ps89:21\">PSA 89:20–89:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:10\">ISA 41:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:13\">ISA 49:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:11\">JER 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:17\">ZEC 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:32\">ACT 20:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:10\">1PE 5:10</a></p>\n<h2>Means by which God encourages believers</h2>\n<h3>Meditation on his law and word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8-Josh1:9\">JOS 1:8–1:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1-Ps1:3\">PSA 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5\">HEB 12:5</a></p>\n<h3>Experience of the Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:16-John14:17\">JHN 14:16–14:17</a></strong> <em>The word used for Spirit here means “Counsellor” or “one who encourages or comforts”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:18–8:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1\">PHP 2:1</a></p>\n<h2>Experience of God's encouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:16-2Cor4:18\">2CO 4:16–4:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:6\">1SA 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:17\">PSA 86:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:9\">ISA 52:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:18-Dan10:19\">DAN 10:18–10:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:31\">ACT 9:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">ACT 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:3-2Cor1:4\">2CO 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:17\">2TI 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18\">HEB 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:5\">HEB 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:3\">1PE 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's encouragement experienced through the words and actions of others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:11\">JDG 7:11</a> <em>Gideon and the dream of the Midianite soldier</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:8\">2CH 15:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:22\">EZR 6:22</a> <em>the returned exiles helped by the king of Assyria</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:15\">ACT 28:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:4\">2CO 7:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:13\">2CO 7:13</a></p>\n<h2>Commands to be encouraged</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:6-Deut31:8\">DEU 31:6–31:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:6-Josh1:8\">JOS 1:6–1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:18\">JOS 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh10:25\">JOS 10:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:13\">1CH 22:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:20\">1CH 28:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:11\">2CH 19:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:7\">2CH 32:7</a> <em>King Hezekiah</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:4\">EZR 10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:14\">PSA 27:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:2\">ISA 54:2</a> <em>growth of the nation of Israel after the exile</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:27\">MAT 14:27</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:50\">MRK 6:50</a>ACT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark27:22\">27:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:25\">ACT 27:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:36\">ACT 27:36</a></p>\n<h2>Effects of being encouraged</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:30-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:30–40:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:3\">PSA 25:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:5\">ROM 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:3\">1CO 14:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:12\">2CO 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:2\">PHP 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:2\">COL 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:11-1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:11–2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Prayers for encouragement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:16-2Thess2:17\">2TH 2:16–2:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:9\">NEH 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:28\">PSA 119:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:14\">ISA 38:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:5-Rom15:6\">ROM 15:5–15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10-Col1:12\">COL 1:10–1:12</a></p>",
